These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia
There 2 different types of food: mango, apricot
1. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Flower           | zinnia | rose |
| Food   | apricot     | mango  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, sudoku
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, prince
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, romance
1. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Cigar   | prince | fonseca    |
| Movie-Genre     | crime | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer
1. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | milk   | 7up |
| Job   | electrician | freelancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, d&b
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, rock-climbing
1. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | reggae |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing    | traveling    |

